{"tid":2386873,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本艦娘玩家程序員洩露代碼 網友：年入300萬不是沒原因","createTime":"2021-01-30T00:59:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T09:19:17.000Z","uid":25345,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"21ef46725f2b6a60c43afaa59e4495071b706a3a","tid":2386873,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T00:59:54.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;年入300萬&rdquo;與&ldquo;年入1500萬&rdquo;這兩個關鍵詞詞條衝上了日推熱搜，引發了大量用戶關注和熱議。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0129%2F761add8dj00qnouno000uc000lh00apg.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0129%252F761add8dj00qnouno000uc000lh00apg.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=e526cbfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  據悉，這兩個關鍵詞源於今天日本發生了兩件社會新聞。其中，&ldquo;年入300萬&rdquo;的消息來源自一位《艦隊collection》玩家，該玩家是一位45歲，並從事20年開發工作但年收入僅300萬日元（約合18萬人民幣）的程序員。因為想要跳槽，但不知從哪兒看到&ldquo;在Github上上傳代碼可以評估年收入&rdquo;的奇葩言論，信以為真。於是他將他負責的包含三井住友銀行，日本最大電信事業集團NTT以及警察廳等大企業的代碼悉數上傳至了GitHub導致代碼洩露。傳聞稱，該玩家因《艦隊collection》在推特上和人對罵後被人人肉，遂代碼洩露事件被人發現。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0129%2F98d2dc44j00qnounq006tc000sg00rmg.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0129%252F98d2dc44j00qnounq006tc000sg00rmg.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=50dfe691&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  而&ldquo;年入1500萬&rdquo;的新聞則來源於日立製作所企劃本部長矢加部太郎，今年52歲，年收入1500萬日元的他因在停車場向女子高中生展示下體，還給對方一張調查表，並還詢問：&ldquo;如果滿分是10分的話，（下體）能夠給幾分？&rdquo;隨後該女子高中生報警將其抓捕。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0129%2F2f74df0fp00qnounq000mc000kk002wg.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0129%252F2f74df0fp00qnounq000mc000kk002wg.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=9bb42657&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  這兩件事的同時發生遭到了日本大量網友的熱議，不少網友認為兩件事形成鮮明的對比，&ldquo;年入300萬的人信息洩露，年入1500萬的人下體洩露&rdquo;對比起來十分生草。一些網友表示：&ldquo;如果是年收入1500萬的程序員，就不會洩露信息了呢。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"ca422b8567f5148b476ed51a220b72edc4956b92","tid":2386873,"uid":142965,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T01:02:14.000Z","msg":"日本人IT真係好廢好落後"},{"pid":"0ac1fb388ecd2b631d61325c22458467a96eecb8","tid":2386873,"uid":258345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T01:21:39.000Z","msg":"日本做IT都係狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da248b4dd23891dd1fe4f723be4ab54674517e51","tid":2386873,"uid":155732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca422b8567f5148b476ed51a220b72edc4956b92","tid":2386873,"uid":142965,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T01:02:14.000Z","msg":"日本人IT真係好廢好落後"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T01:31:02.000Z","msg":"係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日見日文framework教學"},{"pid":"b4ac1e4d73c34fbc1ce04e8a38f619853d590593","tid":2386873,"uid":206617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da248b4dd23891dd1fe4f723be4ab54674517e51","tid":2386873,"uid":155732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca422b8567f5148b476ed51a220b72edc4956b92","tid":2386873,"uid":142965,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T01:02:14.000Z","msg":"日本人IT真係好廢好落後"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T01:31:02.000Z","msg":"係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日見日文framework教學"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T01:36:16.000Z","msg":"同意，之前有段時間都係上日文網學野"},{"pid":"043b2053c4894ad5260eac908cb3d9ee6f036d0f","tid":2386873,"uid":206617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T01:36:27.000Z","msg":"BTW code 呢"},{"pid":"13ee2068e604d04d3f8ca4f4fd9c151473d05c41","tid":2386873,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T01:37:49.000Z","msg":"乜嘢代碼咁巴閉？"},{"pid":"7492f493e3fb23d77a13c8dc55e09393e18e18fb","tid":2386873,"uid":49359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T01:38:52.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">死五毛又出post</span>"},{"pid":"ff62a416c8e99a73d9f1de8bb479cf8fb6244c25","tid":2386873,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T05:57:04.000Z","msg":"1500萬個個咁睇唔開<br />\n做到呢個位<br />\n社會性死亡喎"},{"pid":"f1badad4aad8096bb6f2e6d521e5926b4072d144","tid":2386873,"uid":89939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T06:15:59.000Z","msg":"JK真係好正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a8e8e37df48414c78df3290e4dcf4cd93792c96","tid":2386873,"uid":25345,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T06:28:05.000Z","msg":"300萬個窮撚掌握成堆code公司資產<br />\n1500萬既露下體<br />\n正常應該兩者掉轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76cf5a4dd87052dbc53d8591c0d9702b4c1b65bd","tid":2386873,"uid":68215,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T06:33:46.000Z","msg":"他因在停車場向女子高中生展示下體，還給對方一張調查表，並還詢問：&ldquo;如果滿分是10分的話，（下體）能夠給幾分？&rdquo;<br />\n女：110"},{"pid":"f052fc1fdad75a218da7759d69d575eea973593a","tid":2386873,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a8e8e37df48414c78df3290e4dcf4cd93792c96","tid":2386873,"uid":25345,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T06:28:05.000Z","msg":"300萬個窮撚掌握成堆code公司資產<br />\n1500萬既露下體<br />\n正常應該兩者掉轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T06:46:13.000Z","msg":"當得300萬年薪咁少仲邊會想玩女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bed5f5b4f989c1dbe1760eb5c14149f1123fd190","tid":2386873,"uid":89939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff62a416c8e99a73d9f1de8bb479cf8fb6244c25","tid":2386873,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T05:57:04.000Z","msg":"1500萬個個咁睇唔開<br />\n做到呢個位<br />\n社會性死亡喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T06:57:07.000Z","msg":"升中四了，還未試過拍拖，但毒男說：「不緊要，依家努力讀書考好會考，第時有錢你荒（慌）無女？」<br />\n<br />\n結果，毒男克服了一個又一個的考試，升上大學；影畢業相時，發覺好多人都一雙一對，原來大學係撮合情侶既好地方。毒男依然一個，但他說：「不緊要，即將係我踏入社會大展拳腳既時候，亦係我幸福生活既開始！」<br />\n<br />\n毒男努力工作，三年，五年，七年過去了，依然單身。但他終於達成了心願，成為高收入人仕 － 月薪達一千五百萬yen。<br />\n<br />\n毒男年過五十，開始疑惑：「點解我已經係成功人仕，但仲係無女？」更令他驚訝的是，公司不少女同事都同MK型男拍拖結婚，但那些男人可不是事業型喎，例如，Dorothy既男朋友只係中五畢業既Sales，月薪只有24萬yen，比自己足足少了100萬yen！點解？唔係努力讀書成為有錢人就有女既咩？<br />\n<br />\n不知不覺毒男到了中年，身邊已無什麼朋友，自己渡過一個又一個既聖誕節及情人節。<br />\n<br />\n毒男年老了，孤零零一個坐在公園，回想一生：「自己曾得過什麼？女人的身體是怎麼樣的？和女朋友係海邊共渡平安夜既滋味係點架？高登人不是經常留帖話：『後生時唔好浪費時間，第時有錢你荒無女咩！』我照做了，究竟什麼地方出錯？」"},{"pid":"69f117ed5d6a70f9f7d1448794e4a601b707da96","tid":2386873,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bed5f5b4f989c1dbe1760eb5c14149f1123fd190","tid":2386873,"uid":89939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff62a416c8e99a73d9f1de8bb479cf8fb6244c25","tid":2386873,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T05:57:04.000Z","msg":"1500萬個個咁睇唔開<br />\n做到呢個位<br />\n社會性死亡喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T06:57:07.000Z","msg":"升中四了，還未試過拍拖，但毒男說：「不緊要，依家努力讀書考好會考，第時有錢你荒（慌）無女？」<br />\n<br />\n結果，毒男克服了一個又一個的考試，升上大學；影畢業相時，發覺好多人都一雙一對，原來大學係撮合情侶既好地方。毒男依然一個，但他說：「不緊要，即將係我踏入社會大展拳腳既時候，亦係我幸福生活既開始！」<br />\n<br />\n毒男努力工作，三年，五年，七年過去了，依然單身。但他終於達成了心願，成為高收入人仕 － 月薪達一千五百萬yen。<br />\n<br />\n毒男年過五十，開始疑惑：「點解我已經係成功人仕，但仲係無女？」更令他驚訝的是，公司不少女同事都同MK型男拍拖結婚，但那些男人可不是事業型喎，例如，Dorothy既男朋友只係中五畢業既Sales，月薪只有24萬yen，比自己足足少了100萬yen！點解？唔係努力讀書成為有錢人就有女既咩？<br />\n<br />\n不知不覺毒男到了中年，身邊已無什麼朋友，自己渡過一個又一個既聖誕節及情人節。<br />\n<br />\n毒男年老了，孤零零一個坐在公園，回想一生：「自己曾得過什麼？女人的身體是怎麼樣的？和女朋友係海邊共渡平安夜既滋味係點架？高登人不是經常留帖話：『後生時唔好浪費時間，第時有錢你荒無女咩！』我照做了，究竟什麼地方出錯？」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T07:08:49.000Z","msg":"呢個故事假的<br />\n有這個財力<br />\n可找廿幾,三十歲女,雖然可能只係愛你d錢"},{"pid":"3cb3620ac5b6c6b61e5bb44081baa63136cedbce","tid":2386873,"uid":25073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76cf5a4dd87052dbc53d8591c0d9702b4c1b65bd","tid":2386873,"uid":68215,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T06:33:46.000Z","msg":"他因在停車場向女子高中生展示下體，還給對方一張調查表，並還詢問：&ldquo;如果滿分是10分的話，（下體）能夠給幾分？&rdquo;<br />\n女：110"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T09:19:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}